high_descs: Walk to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife off of the counter.
Walk to the loaf of bread on the counter in front of the microwave.
Slice the loaf of bread with the knife.
Take the knife to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Go back to the loaf of bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the loaf.
Go to the microwave with the slice of bread.
Cook the slice of bread in the microwave.
Walk over to the counter in front of the spoon.
Place the slice of bread on the counter by the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooked slice of bread on the counter by the spoon.

high_descs: Go to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Go to the counter above the dishwasher.
Slice the bread on the counter.
Look up at the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Move down to the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Move to the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Take the warm bread to the counter on the right of the microwave.
Set the bread on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm slice of bread on the counter.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife that is behind the lettuce on the counter.
With the knife in hand go to the dishwasher.
Slice half the loaf of bread that is on the counter.
Move to the microwave.
Open the door. Place the knife in the microwave and close the door.
Turn and go the the bread that is sliced on the counter to your right.
Pick up the middle slice of bread.
With the slice of bread in hand move to your left in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave. Place the slice of bread behind the knife on the right side.  Close door and star microwave. When finished open door and grab slice of bread.
With the slice of bread in your hand Turn right and go straight to where the lettuce is on the counter.  Turn left to face counter.
Place the slice of bread on the back counter shelf standing up right behind the fork.
anns.task_desc: Slice bread and warm it up to place on counter.
